&lt;section class="ap-about"&gt;
&lt;h2 class="ap-h2"&gt;About Me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I started using Linux pretty young and it genuinely got me interested. The more I learned, the more I wanted to dig deeper. A mentor of mine who was Red Hat certified pointed me toward the Red Hat track, and that's what set the direction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since then I've been working my way through it properly: hands-on labs, real certs, and actually managing servers, cloud environments, and deployments along the way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
